targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  AVG(CAST(is_correct AS INT64)) AS avg_prediction_accuracy
FROM
  `dog_prediction_app.prediction_metrics`
WHERE model_version = '${model_version_A}'

SELECT
  model_version, AVG(CAST(is_correct AS INT64)) AS avg_prediction_accuracy
FROM
  `dog_prediction_app.prediction_metrics`
  GROUP BY model_version
  ORDER BY model_version

SELECT
  AVG(CAST(is_correct AS INT64)) AS avg_prediction_accuracy
FROM
  `dog_prediction_app.prediction_metrics`
WHERE model_version = '${model_version_B}'

WITH correct_preds AS (
  SELECT actual, model_version, COUNT(*) AS num_correct
  FROM creature-vision.dog_prediction_app.prediction_metrics
  WHERE is_correct = true
  GROUP BY model_version, actual
),
incorrect_preds AS (
  SELECT actual, model_version, COUNT(*) AS num_incorrect
  FROM creature-vision.dog_prediction_app.prediction_metrics
  WHERE is_correct = false
  GROUP BY model_version, actual
),
model_summary AS (
  SELECT
    COALESCE(cp.model_version, ip.model_version) AS model_version,
    COALESCE(cp.actual, ip.actual) AS actual,
    SUM(IFNULL(cp.num_correct, 0)) AS total_correct_predictions,
    SUM(IFNULL(ip.num_incorrect, 0)) AS total_incorrect_predictions
  FROM correct_preds cp
  FULL OUTER JOIN incorrect_preds ip
    ON cp.model_version = ip.model_version AND cp.actual = ip.actual
  GROUP BY model_version, actual
)
SELECT *, CONCAT(model_version, ' : ', actual) AS model_class
FROM model_summary
WHERE actual IN (${class})
AND model_version in (${model_versions})
ORDER BY model_version, actual DESC

SELECT
  model_version,
  class_label AS actual,
  example_count,
  run_timestamp,
  CONCAT(model_version, ' : ', class_label) AS model_class
FROM (
  SELECT *,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY model_version, class_label
      ORDER BY run_timestamp DESC
    ) AS row_num
  FROM `creature-vision.dataset_distribution.class_distribution`
  WHERE model_version IN (${model_versions})
    AND class_label IN (${class})
)
WHERE row_num = 1
ORDER BY model_version, actual DESC

WITH latest_runs AS (
  SELECT
    model_version,
    class_label,
    label_id,
    example_count,
    run_timestamp,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY model_version, class_label
      ORDER BY run_timestamp DESC
    ) AS row_num
  FROM
    `creature-vision.dataset_distribution.class_distribution`
)

SELECT
  model_version,
  class_label,
  example_count
FROM
  latest_runs
WHERE
  row_num = 1
  AND model_version = '${model_version_A}'
ORDER BY
  example_count,
  class_label

SELECT
  TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(timestamp, HOUR) AS time,
  AVG(CAST(is_correct AS INT64)) AS accuracy,
  model_version
FROM
  `dog_prediction_app.prediction_metrics`
WHERE
  timestamp BETWEEN TIMESTAMP('${__from:date}') AND TIMESTAMP('${__to:date}')
  AND model_version IN (${model_versions:sqlstring})
GROUP BY
  time, model_version
ORDER BY
  time
